    {"type":"text","id":"insight_text","x":40,"y":542,"width":1030,"height":56,"text":"Why AsyncGenerator wins: push-based (immediate yield), type-safe (compile-time Stream<T>),\nbackpressure-ready (natural pause/resume), cancellable (return/throw), no polling overhead.\nClaude Code uses it for 220+ event types across a complete session — not just text streaming.","originalText":"Why AsyncGenerator wins: push-based (immediate yield), type-safe (compile-time Stream<T>),\nbackpressure-ready (natural pause/resume), cancellable (return/throw), no polling overhead.\nClaude Code uses it for 220+ event types across a complete session — not just text streaming.","fontSize":10,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"middle","strokeColor":"#6C63FF","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"seed":600003,"version":1,"versionNonce":600004,"isDeleted":false,"groupIds":[],"boundElements":null,"link":null,"locked":false,"containerId":"insight_box","lineHeight":1.25}
